WEBVTT

00:03:59.803 --> 00:04:03.316
in se ujameš v vzorec lažnih novic,

00:04:03.340 --> 00:04:04.930
postaneš sokrivec.

00:04:05.658 --> 00:04:09.439
In jaz ne želim
nositi breme krivde za genocid.

00:04:09.439 --> 00:04:11.962
(Aplavz)

00:04:14.402 --> 00:04:17.180
Že od nekdaj se bijejo propagandne bitke,

00:04:17.204 --> 00:04:21.230
v katerih si nastopila pogumno
kot v tistih časih.

00:04:21.652 --> 00:04:25.379
Vendar gre dandanes za povsem nov način

00:04:25.403 --> 00:04:27.607
spreminjanja novic v lažne.

00:04:27.631 --> 00:04:29.265
Kako bi ga opisala?

00:04:29.289 --> 00:04:31.373
Poglej, resnično sem zaskrbljena.